snippet.textDisplay: As a Chelsea fan I applaud arsenal for playing their asses off. They had a man down and still managed to get a draw. This Chelsea team has been such a disappointment this season. Started out very promising but now you can clearly see everything wrong with the team.. Hudson isn’t 100% he lacks so much and it’s going to take a season or two to get back to how he was. That Injury did set him back. Abraham isn’t a world class striker. Idk how many shots he had but all of them straight to Leno. We have nothing up to when it comes to scoring and creating. We need a better striker and someone else in our midfield and we need better fullbacks. I’m hoping we get some players to compete for those spots because we desperately need the back up.
